high_descs: Turn left turn right turn left. Go forward, turn to the left  in front of the spoon in the bowl.
Pick up the spoon That is in the bowl.
Turn left, then turn right, In front of the stove.
Stop in front of the stove.
Pick up the Pan that is on the stove.
Turn around then walked forward towards the ice maker then  turn left to face the sink
Walk to the sink and put the Pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the pan off of the stove and put it in the sink

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter with the coffee maker on it, turn left to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the spoon behind the tomato on the right.
Walk to the front of the stove on the left.
Put the spoon down in the pan on the front right burner.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the pan down inside of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a pan, and put the pan inside of the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to face the corner of the counter.
Pick up the spoon at the back of the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the stove.
Place the spoon on the pan on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pan with a spoon in it.
Turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the pan with a spoon in it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a spoon in a pan plus move them to the sink.
